  "summary": "Malicious code in @corpweb-ui/wmkt-library (npm)",
  "details": "On installation the package's preinstall hook runs index.js, which executes system reconnaissance commands (whoami, hostname, uname -a, and curl to ifconfig[.]me to learn the public IP), formats the output as a fake \"VERISIGN - DEEP RCE CONFIRMED\" banner, and exfiltrates the data to a Telegram bot (hxxps://api[.]telegram[.]org) using a hardcoded bot token and chat_id 1483949647. Code comments describe the attack intent.",
